   </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include ('partials/navbar') %>

    

    <div class="container" style=" width: 80%; margin: 20px auto">
        <h1><%= curso.nombre %></h1>

        <div class="course-container">
            <div class="course-content">
                <img src="/images/graduates.jpg" alt="Graduates" class="course-image">
                <p>
                    Tempor erat elitr at rebum at at clita. Diam dolor diam ipsum sit amet diam et eos labore. 
                    Clita erat ipsum et lorem et sit, sed stet lorem sit clita duo justo magna dolore erat amet.
